4 年第三季度) 的营业利润下降了 27%。再加上 SE 的高端游戏销售同比下滑，这一下降可能是导致投资者抛售股票，进而导致股价暴跌的原因。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-bc22d7405723c98210ac8ed32015bc54_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "99 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4121144249"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1/3y6LfS56lVEAMaCTExMTgwMDgzMiDOtNW5BjAAODNAA3IKNDEyMTE0NDI0OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1731804943.267631", "card_id": "Q_598821148", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "猪为什么是蛇的天敌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a3748985dcb1ec1c4c498004795956ae_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/598821148"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1/3y6LfS56lVEAMaCDk1MzUxODI1ILS5xqIGMAA4mQFABHIJNTk4ODIxMTQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1731804943.267881", "card_id": "Q_4270823674", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我发现 35-40 岁中年人找工作不太好找，年龄都卡在 40 岁，这是为什么呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "35-40 岁难道就没有选择工作的机会吗？企业是如何选择人才的？难道仅仅凭年龄吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4270823674"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1/3y6LfS56lVE